output: PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/> PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> SELECT ?var1 WHERE { ?var1 wdt:location wd:San Antonio . ?var1 wdt:instance of wd:battle . ?var1 wdt:point in time ?var0 . FILTER( YEAR(?var0) = 1836 ) }
